These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: subway, trike, quad-bike, motorbike, skateboard, tram, car
There 7 different types of food: apple, corn, cranberry, kale, peas, peach, lime
There are 7 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, juice, milk, iced-tea, lemonade, 7up
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is between the person eating corn and the person eating apple##2
 4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person eating corn is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 6. the person driving the subway is the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person eating kale is between the person drinking milk and the person driving the skateboard##2
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person driving the car is the person eating cranberry##1
11. the person eating peach is the person driving the motorbike##1
12. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
13. the person drinking tea is the person eating peas##1
14. the person driving the tram is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking 7up##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Transport   | skateboard | subway     | tram | trike | motorbike | car  | quad-bike  |
| Food   | apple  | kale        | corn  | lime     | peach   | cranberry       | peas   |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate   | 7up | milk    | juice  | iced-tea | lemonade | tea |

