.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: disaster, family, horror, superhero, spy, scientific, musical
There 7 different types of food: corn, lettuce, grapes, avocado, peach, broccoli, papaya
House: gothic-revival, colonial, modern, craftsman, wooden, futuristic, ranch-style
 1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the colonial house##1
 2. the person eating peach is the person eating peach##1
 3. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 4. the person eating avocado is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 5. the person eating corn is the person watching musical movies##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is the craftsman house##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is between the person eating papaya and the ranch-style house##2
 8. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 9. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
10. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the wooden house##1
11. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the gothic-revival house is the person watching family movies##1
13. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
14. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the futuristic house##1
15. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
16. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | musical      | superhero     | disaster  | spy | horror | family |
| Food         | lettuce  | corn | broccoli | grapes | papaya | avocado   | peach  |
| House     | modern   | futuristic     | ranch-style        | craftsman  | wooden   | colonial       | gothic-revival      |

