.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dannemann, swisher, game, montecristo, vegafina, old-henry
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: iris, amaryllis, lily, rose, poppy, daffodil, zinnia
There 7 different types of food: cauliflower, kale, strawberry, kiwi, spinach, orange, tomato
 1. the person eating kale is the person who growsiris##1
 2. the person eating spinach is the person who growsrose##1
 3. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is the dannemann-smoker##1
 5. the person eating orange is between the person eating tomato and the person who growszinnia##2
 6. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 8. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
10. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
11. the person eating kale is the person who growsiris##1
12. the person who growslily is on the right of the game-smoker##1
13. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
14. the person eating tomato is the old-henry-smoker##1
15. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Cigar    | bluemaster     | montecristo   | vegafina        | dannemann   | swisher     | game     | old-henry    |
