7 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, dunhill, bolivar, alhambra, old-henry, dannemann, cain
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: iris, daffodil, dahlia, orchid, zinnia, rose, tulip
 1. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
 2. the dannemann-smoker is the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is the alhambra-smoker##1
 4. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
 7. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
 8. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the person who growsrose is the ritmeester-smoker##1
10. the person who growsiris is the person playing go##1
11. the bolivar-smoker is the person who growstulip##1
12. the person playing bridge is the person who growszinnia##1
13. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1
14. the cain-smoker is between the bolivar-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##2
15. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Game          | bridge  | canasta    | go  | domino | snooker  | monopoly | whist |
| Cigar   | old-henry | bolivar | cain   | alhambra   | dannemann | ritmeester     | dunhill |
