There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, almond-milk, mirinda, cola, hot-chocolate, lemonade
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the cape-cod house is the owner of the goat##1
 4. the cottage house is the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is the gothic-revival house##1
 7. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the victorian house##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the victorian house is on the right of the cottage house##1
12. the person drinking cola is between the victorian house and the ranch-style house##2
13. the owner of the fish is on the right of the victorian house##1
14. the person drinking milk is the owner of the hamster##1
15. the cape-cod house is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
16. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| House           | cottage | victorian    | farmhouse    | ranch-style  | cape-cod | gothic-revival | art-deco |
