 1. the fan ambient is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 2. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 3. the fan reggae is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 5. the person who likes black is the fan electronic##1
 6. the fan indie is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes chestnut##2
 7. the person who likes yellow is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the fan rock##1
 9. the fan rock is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
10. the fan electronic is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
11. the person who likes red is the fan d&b##1
12. the person who likes red is the fan d&b##1
13. the fan ambient is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
14. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
15. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |   4    |      5      |       6        |       7       |
